00:57:48,279 --> 00:57:50,799
I'm calling this
Worse Things Happen at Sea.

1264
00:57:50,879 --> 00:57:52,879
[all laughing]

1265
00:57:52,960 --> 00:57:56,359
- We did get your flashing lighthouse.
